A na-ahụ ya n'ebe niile n'akụkụ ndị na-ekpo ọkụ nke Western Hemisphere, a kọrọ ya site na ndịda Mexico (Chiapas, Campeche, Quintana Roo, Tabasco, Veracruz), Central America, ndịda Florida, Greater Antilles, Trinidad, ugwu South America. A makwaara ya site na aha ndị ama ama Brassia, spider orchid na cricket orchid.
